我把这些放进衣橱里吧？
I'll put these in the closet, sir?

567
00:41:03,045 --> 00:41:04,672
好
Yeah, fine.

568
00:42:06,345 --> 00:42:08,055
（圣巴托罗缪街口）

569
00:42:08,222 --> 00:42:10,391
（地铁系统 出入隧道）

570
00:42:10,558 --> 00:42:12,059
（通风口）

571
00:42:15,396 --> 00:42:16,897
（教堂隧道）

572
00:42:39,516 --> 00:42:42,311
今天的纽约很庄严
A solemn day here in New York City.

573
00:42:42,478 --> 00:42:45,397
麦克斯韦·奥兹副总统的葬礼
The funeral of Vice President Maxwell Oates,

574
00:42:45,564 --> 00:42:49,318
五任参议员兼冷战斗士
a former five-term U.S. senator and Cold War warrior

575
00:42:49,480 --> 00:42:50,686
他最伟大的遗产
whose greatest legacy

576
00:42:50,830 --> 00:42:54,692
可能是缔造出美俄关系的新纪元
may be as architect of the new era of Russian-American relations.

577
00:42:55,490 --> 00:42:57,575
俄罗斯总统鲍里斯·马特维耶夫
Russian president Boris Matveyev

578
00:42:57,740 --> 00:43:00,656
自莫斯科来此担任名誉扶棺人
has journeyed from Moscow to be an honorary pallbearer

579
00:43:00,710 --> 00:43:04,342
向他西方世界最伟大的朋友致意
to the man he's called his greatest friend in the West.

580
00:44:02,683 --> 00:44:05,019
戒备范围多大？
What's the security perimeter?

581
00:44:05,185 --> 00:44:08,230
两层人墙 整个街区都在控制中
We're two deep inside and we own this entire block.

582
00:44:08,397 --> 00:44:11,734
这些还是特勤人员 不是中情局的
And those are Secret Service agents, not CIA.

583
00:44:11,900 --> 00:44:15,362
放心拉 真有趣
So relax. That's real funny.

584
00:44:15,904 --> 00:44:18,073
我不知道你们还会开玩笑
Didn't know you guys told jokes.

585
00:44:22,036 --> 00:44:23,162
全体 立定
Detail, halt.

586
00:44:25,414 --> 00:44:27,583
向前 走
Forward, march.

587
00:44:44,430 --> 00:44:45,674
由于葬礼
Due to the funeral,

588
00:44:45,773 --> 00:44:48,520
51街地铁站关闭
the 51st Street station is closed.

589
00:44:52,190 --> 00:44:54,590
重复：由于葬礼
Repeat: Due to the funeral,

590
00:44:54,692 --> 00:44:57,360
51街地铁站关闭
the 51st Street station is closed.

591
00:45:01,617 --> 00:45:03,619
什么…？ 嘿 这怎么回事？
What--? Hey, what's going on?

592
00:45:03,786 --> 00:45:05,204
有烟
There's smoke.

593
00:45:07,370 --> 00:45:08,579
退后 退后
Step back, step back.

594
00:45:08,648 --> 00:45:10,500
大家让开
Everybody, move out of the way.

595
00:45:44,993 --> 00:45:47,287
伊莲诺 看到你真好
Eleanor. Good to see you.

596
00:45:47,830 --> 00:45:49,581
谢谢
Thank you.

597
00:45:52,370 --> 00:45:53,257
鲍里斯
Boris.

598
00:45:53,346 --> 00:45:54,855
总统先生
Mr. President.

599
00:45:59,842 --> 00:46:01,385
你好
Hello.

600
00:46:12,396 --> 00:46:14,606
请坐下
Please be seated.

601
00:46:26,618 --> 00:46:29,204
静候总统致词
Stand by for president's speech.

602
00:46:30,910 --> 00:46:32,524
巡视教堂周边
Patrolling church exterior.

603
00:46:32,670 --> 00:46:35,370
侧门不准任何人进出
No one in or out the side doors.

604
00:46:36,962 --> 00:46:38,130
奥兹先生
Mrs. Oates.

605
00:46:39,710 --> 00:46:40,742
伊莲诺
Eleanor,

606
00:46:41,210 --> 00:46:42,228
乔
Joe,

607
00:46:42,411 --> 00:46:43,300
玛丽莎 唐纳德…
Marissa, Donald...

608
00:46:43,460 --> 00:46:45,555
总统讲完后 唱诗班唱歌
After the president, the choir sings,

609
00:46:45,652 --> 00:46:47,500
然后马特维耶夫宣讲颂辞
then Matveyev delivers the eulogy.

610
00:46:47,723 --> 00:46:50,893
要是你手下敢作乱 那一定要惊天动地
If your girl tries anything here, it'd have to be pretty amazing.

611
00:46:55,270 --> 00:46:59,263
我早知他的贡献绝对超群绝伦
I knew he would bring more to the job than just his years of experience.

612
00:47:00,235 --> 00:47:02,362
身为副总统
As vice president,

613
00:47:02,520 --> 00:47:04,358
他让全世界看到了…
he showed the world the best...

614
00:47:04,579 --> 00:47:06,543
美国人的典范
of what it is to be an American.

615
00:47:07,576 --> 00:47:08,869
而今天
And today,

616
00:47:09,036 --> 00:47:13,790
世界向一位伟人道别
the world says goodbye to a great man.

617
00:47:23,133 --> 00:47:24,760
我去检查后面
I'll check the back.

618
00:47:24,927 --> 00:47:27,262
LZ4  没问题
Lima Zulu 4, clear.

619
00:47:53,288 --> 00:47:55,624
我与麦克斯韦·奥兹的友谊
My friendship with Maxwell Oates

620
00:47:55,791 --> 00:47:58,794
开启于最不可能的地方
began in the unlikeliest of places:

621
00:47:58,961 --> 00:48:00,837
LZ4  请说
Lima Zulu 4, come in.

622
00:48:01,004 --> 00:48:02,881
在谈判桌上
Across the negotiating table...

623
00:48:03,048 --> 00:48:04,800
回报状况 LZ4
What's your status, Lima Zulu 4?

624
00:48:04,967 --> 00:48:06,176
两员失联
We got two MIAs.

625
00:48:06,340 --> 00:48:10,684
LZ4在地窑入口外侧隧道 还有LZ5
Lima Zulu 4 in the utility tunnel outside the crypt entrance and Lima Zulu 5.

626
00:48:11,640 --> 00:48:13,095
我正下到地窖去
I'm heading down to the crypt.

627
00:48:13,208 --> 00:48:14,760
下面出了状况
Some kind of trouble down there.

628
00:48:14,935 --> 00:48:16,562
怎么回事？快回答
What's going on, guys? Talk to me.

629
00:48:16,728 --> 00:48:19,856
LZ1、2、3在地窖会合 重复
Subunits Lima Zulu 1, 2 and 3, converge on the crypt. Repeat:

630
00:48:20,023 --> 00:48:21,108
在地窖会合
Converge on the crypt.

631
00:48:21,275 --> 00:48:23,318
他成就非凡
He made all the difference, and for that,

632
00:48:23,485 --> 00:48:28,365
因此他获得我的尊崇与景仰
he will always have my respect and admiration.

633
00:49:15,203 --> 00:49:17,164
那也是我朋友麦克斯韦·奥兹会说的
That is what my friend Maxwell Oates would have said.

634
00:49:23,962 --> 00:49:25,130
老天
What's going on?

635
00:49:35,974 --> 00:49:37,517
马特维耶夫
Matveyev.

636
00:49:38,393 --> 00:49:39,561
去救马特维耶夫
Get goddamn Matveyev.

637
00:49:54,701 --> 00:49:57,371
- 叫炸弹小组来！ - 快 快！
- Get the bomb squad in here! - Go, go!

638
00:50:37,077 --> 00:50:38,787
放下！
Drop it!

639
00:50:40,789 --> 00:50:41,832
放下！
Drop it!

640
00:50:48,755 --> 00:50:52,050
- 这里有医护人员吗？ - 我看到她了
- Any MTs down here? - I see her.

641
00:50:52,126 --> 00:50:53,117
把手举起来！
Keep your hands up!

642
00:50:53,459 --> 00:50:54,970
枪手在12点方向
Shooter's at 12 o'clock.

643
00:50:55,130 --> 00:50:57,798
- 枪！她有枪！她有枪！ - 别动！
- Gun! She's got a gun. She has a gun! - Don't move!

644
00:50:58,550 --> 00:51:00,551
- 不准动！不准动！ - 把手举高！
- Do not move! Do not move! - Keep your hands up!

645
00:51:00,934 --> 00:51:02,561
逮捕她 逮捕她！
Take her down, take her down!

646
00:51:02,728 --> 00:51:04,187
检查其它武器
Check for other weapons.

647
00:51:05,397 --> 00:51:07,607
立刻派医疗小组来地窖
We need a medical crew in the crypt immediately.

648
00:51:07,774 --> 00:51:09,568
我摸不到脉搏
I can't feel a pulse.

649
00:51:11,319 --> 00:51:12,654
退后 退后
Back it up! Back it up!

650
00:51:12,821 --> 00:51:15,782
继续走 继续走 继续走
Come on, guys. Keep moving. Keep moving. Keep moving.

651
00:51:16,992 --> 00:51:18,201
快走 快走
Let's go, let's go.

652
00:51:18,702 --> 00:51:20,412
小心这家伙
Hey, watch this guy, watch this guy.

653
00:51:20,579 --> 00:51:21,621
- 退开！ - 继续走
- Back up! - Keep moving.

654
00:51:21,788 --> 00:51:23,039
退开！
Sir, back up!

655
00:51:23,206 --> 00:51:25,792
为什么？为什么？！
Why? Why?!

656
00:51:27,502 --> 00:51:30,255
你知道你手上染了多少血吗？
Do you have any idea how much blood is on your hands?

657
00:51:30,422 --> 00:51:32,007
你等着死在黑牢里吧
You're gonna rot in a hole, Salt.

658
00:51:32,174 --> 00:51:34,176
我会亲自确认这件事 最黑的黑牢
I'm gonna see to it personally! A dark hole!

659
00:51:34,342 --> 00:51:35,844
你控制一下
Get ahold of yourself.

660
00:51:36,511 --> 00:51:38,013
开门 开门
Get the door, get the door.

661
00:51:38,180 --> 00:51:40,849
- 放开我！  - 退开！退开！
- Get off me! - Back off, man! Back off!

662
00:51:41,016 --> 00:51:42,350
好了 走吧
That's it. Let's go.

663
00:51:43,477 --> 00:51:45,353
往后站
Stand back.

664
00:51:46,062 --> 00:51:48,607
关门！快 快！
Close it! Go, go, go!

665
00:52:00,869 --> 00:52:04,372
马特维耶夫在送医途中宣告死亡
Matveyev was declared dead en route to the hospital.

666
00:52:04,831 --> 00:52:06,166
老天爷
Jesus Christ.

667
00:52:06,583 --> 00:52:07,751
还好
Yeah.

668
00:52:08,043 --> 00:52:10,086
你没错看她
You were right about her.

669
00:52:11,046 --> 00:52:13,590
她有机会杀我
She had the drop on me, Ted.

670
00:52:14,925 --> 00:52:16,676
她为什么不开枪？
Why didn't she shoot?

671
00:53:10,146 --> 00:53:12,440
员警受伤！注意！
Cop down, cop down! Hear me!

672
00:54:00,730 --> 00:54:02,499
下车
Get out of the car

673
00:54:02,623 --> 00:54:04,990
把手放头上！
with your hands on your head!

674
00:54:05,201 --> 00:54:07,996
快点！手举起来！
Right now! Hands in the air!

675
00:54:25,055 --> 00:54:28,725
- 你看到没？ - 快叫那些人来帮忙
- Hey, did you see that? - Hey, get those guys over here.

676
00:54:28,892 --> 00:54:31,186
叫他们来帮忙
Get them over here to help.

677
00:54:46,201 --> 00:54:48,787
快来帮我把他弄出来 快帮忙
Somebody help me get him out. Help me get him out.

678
00:55:20,735 --> 00:55:22,070
你叫什么名字？
What is your name?

679
00:55:22,237 --> 00:55:24,739
我就叫伊芙·绍特
My name is Evelyn Salt.

680
00:55:24,906 --> 00:55:26,616
你要念哪一家学校？
What college will you attend?

681
00:55:26,783 --> 00:55:28,660
普林斯顿大学
Princeton University.

682
00:55:28,827 --> 00:55:30,036
你要去哪工作？
Where will you work?

683
00:55:30,203 --> 00:55:32,205
中央情报局
The Central Intelligence Agency.

684
00:55:32,372 --> 00:55:34,082
你要信任谁？
Who will you trust?

685
00:55:34,249 --> 00:55:35,959
谁都不信
No one.

686
00:55:36,126 --> 00:55:38,503
要有耐心
Be very patient.

687
00:55:38,670 --> 00:55:40,422
要记得你的训练
Remember your training.

688
00:55:41,339 --> 00:55:44,592
要记得你并不是唯一的一个
Remember, you're not the only one.

689
00:55:44,759 --> 00:55:46,344
还有很多人
There are many others.

690
00:55:46,511 --> 00:55:49,806
你们全都在等待出击
All of you waiting to strike.

691
00:55:49,973 --> 00:55:52,100
- 是的  - 我们会出击
- Yes.  - And we will strike.

692
00:55:52,760 --> 00:55:54,091
一起联手
Together.

693
00:55:54,532 --> 00:55:55,930
对
Yes.

694
00:55:58,565 --> 00:56:00,025
等等
Wait.

695
00:56:02,770 --> 00:56:03,870
有一天
One day,

696
00:56:04,151 --> 00:56:06,690
我会去找你们
I will come for all of you.

697
00:56:12,787 --> 00:56:14,581
你好 伊芙
Hello, Evelyn.

698
00:56:14,914 --> 00:56:18,084
我是美国大使馆的科伦萧
I'm Martin Crenshaw from the U.S. Embassy.

699
00:56:18,752 --> 00:56:22,130
对于你们的意外我们很遗憾
We're very sorry about your family's accident.

700
00:56:29,220 --> 00:56:33,058
美国大使馆外的暴民声援他们新领袖的发言
Rioters outside the U.S. Embassy cheered their new leader's words

701
00:56:33,224 --> 00:56:36,728
并要求他采取强烈行动
and called on him to take strong action against what they are calling

702
00:56:36,895 --> 00:56:40,607
反击一桩由美国主导的恐怖行动
a state-sponsored act of terrorism on the part of the U.S.

703
00:56:40,774 --> 00:56:42,817
这些暴民在俄罗斯各地
These riots are sparking similar outbreaks

704
00:56:42,984 --> 00:56:46,154
激起类似的反美游行
of anti-American protests across Russia.

705
00:56:46,321 --> 00:56:49,491
新任俄罗斯总统说过 “我们要复仇”
"We will strike back," says the new Russian president,

706
00:56:49,657 --> 00:56:52,077
愤怒指责在今天由美国情报员
angrily condemning today's assassination

707
00:56:52,243 --> 00:56:55,705
伊芙·绍特所主导的暗杀行动
by American intelligence officer Evelyn Salt.

708
00:56:56,280 --> 00:56:58,606
纵使马特维耶夫总统的遗体
As the body of slain President Matveyev

709
00:56:58,670 --> 00:56:59,870
正在运往莫斯科的途中
is on its way back to Moscow,

710
00:57:00,043 --> 00:57:02,629
俄罗斯各地仍爆发反美暴动
anti-American riots have erupted across Russia,

711
00:57:02,796 --> 00:57:05,507
美国外交官车辆在莫斯科遇袭
with bombings of U.S. diplomats' cars in Moscow.

712
00:57:06,841 --> 00:57:09,761
俄罗斯武装部队进入高度警戒
The Russian armed forces have been put on high alert.

713
00:57:10,220 --> 00:57:12,972
为因应急速扩大的危机
Responding to a rapidly escalating crisis,

714
00:57:13,139 --> 00:57:16,351
路易斯总统召集紧急白宫会议
President Lewis has called for an emergency White House meeting

715
00:57:16,518 --> 00:57:19,938
内阁、军方领袖与北约代表均出席
with cabinet members, military leaders and NATO representatives.

716
00:57:20,021 --> 00:57:22,933
你好 契诃夫同志

717
00:57:23,507 --> 00:57:25,217
（俄语）你好 奥洛夫同志

718
00:57:29,197 --> 00:57:32,117
我在华盛顿看到你时 差点失控
When I saw you in Washington, I almost ran to you.

719
00:57:39,541 --> 00:57:42,252
你不该结婚的
You were not supposed to get married.

720
00:57:42,418 --> 00:57:46,840
除非结婚能带来策略性的优点
Not unless it had great tactical advantage.

721
00:57:47,006 --> 00:57:48,716
我结婚是为了看起来正常
I did it to seem normal.

722
00:57:49,551 --> 00:57:51,553
你今天逃走时 我心想
When you escaped today, I thought:

723
00:57:51,710 --> 00:57:55,434
就连我也没想到你有这么行
"Even I could not have hoped for so much."

724
00:57:56,307 --> 00:57:59,936
你是我最神的创作
You are my greatest creation.

725
00:58:01,104 --> 00:58:03,273
是你把我训练的好
You trained me well.

726
00:58:39,767 --> 00:58:42,896
我丈夫 在你手里？
My husband, you have him?

727
00:58:43,062 --> 00:58:45,440
我必须要确认
I had to be certain.

728
00:58:45,607 --> 00:58:47,692
现在你信任我了？
But now you trust me?

729
00:58:47,859 --> 00:58:48,902
完全信任
Completely.

730
00:58:57,118 --> 00:59:01,039
那么告诉我接下来要做什么
So tell me what's next.

731
00:59:01,289 --> 00:59:03,541
接下来 第二阶段：
Next, part two:

732
00:59:04,042 --> 00:59:08,046
控制这国家的核子武器
We seize control of this country's atomic weapons.

733
00:59:08,963 --> 00:59:10,340
怎么做？
How?

734
01:01:44,285 --> 01:01:46,245
我将不会再与你联络
You won't hear from me again,

735
01:01:46,788 --> 01:01:48,081
我的女儿
my daughter.

736
01:03:44,614 --> 01:03:47,033
厮守终身
Forever and ever.

737
01:04:19,899 --> 01:04:21,609
契诃夫
Chenkov.

738
01:04:23,152 --> 01:04:24,779
你记得我吗？
Do you remember me?

739
01:04:30,117 --> 01:04:31,244
契诃夫
Chenkov.

740
01:04:32,620 --> 01:04:34,288
你有想过我吗？
Did you miss me?

741
01:04:34,830 --> 01:04:36,040
史奈德？
Shnaider?

742
01:04:40,586 --> 01:04:41,879
你来这里多久了？
How long have you been here?

743
01:04:44,290 --> 01:04:46,623
我在你之后一年离开俄国
I left Russia one year after you.

744
01:04:46,871 --> 01:04:48,340
到了布拉格
To Prague.

745
01:04:48,594 --> 01:04:52,223
我担任北约对白宫联络官三年了
I've been the NATO liaison to the White House for three years.

746
01:04:52,640 --> 01:04:55,309
艾德华·托马斯上校
Colonel Edward Tomas.

747
01:04:55,643 --> 01:04:58,813
你是我的随员
And you are my attache.

748
01:04:58,980 --> 01:05:00,648
你的证件
Your ID.

749
01:05:01,315 --> 01:05:03,651
不用担心 我们有的是时间
Don't worry, we have plenty of time.

750
01:05:03,818 --> 01:05:06,737
更重要的是我们的任务
More importantly, our mission.

751
01:05:07,437 --> 01:05:11,045
地下调堡就在白宫地下第八层
The bunker eight stories below the White House.

752
01:05:13,494 --> 01:05:15,246
那就是总统要去的地方
That's where the president needs to be.

753
01:05:20,501 --> 01:05:21,669
要怎么做？
How do we do it?

754
01:05:21,830 --> 01:05:23,986
别担心 他会去的 那是我的任务
Don't worry, he'll be there. That's my job.

755
01:05:24,171 --> 01:05:25,920
我要确保他会去
I'll make sure he's there.

756
01:05:26,750 --> 01:05:28,160
那我的任务呢？
What's my job?

757
01:05:28,642 --> 01:05:30,210
你还记得吗 契诃夫
Do you remember, Chenkov,

758
01:05:30,380 --> 01:05:31,550
我们还年轻时
when we were young

759
01:05:31,666 --> 01:05:34,140
你每一件事都要拿第一名
and you had to finish first in everything?

760
01:05:34,307 --> 01:05:36,058
每件事都要做到最好
Had to be the best at everything.

761
01:05:36,151 --> 01:05:39,795
尽管明明知道你要挨揍 你也要抢第一
Though you knew you would be beaten with a cane, you had to finish first.

762
01:05:40,438 --> 01:05:42,023
我记得
I remember.

763
01:05:42,189 --> 01:05:45,693
今晚 你又会抢在我前面了
Tonight you will finish ahead of me again.

764
01:05:48,518 --> 01:05:52,154
今晚 你要毙掉美国总统
Tonight you will kill America's president.

765
01:06:05,546 --> 01:06:07,381
请出示证件
IDs, please.

766
01:06:08,049 --> 01:06:10,176
打开引擎盖和后车厢
Pop the hood and open the trunk.

767
01:06:10,551 --> 01:06:12,094
我检查旁边
I'll check the side.

768
01:06:12,119 --> 01:06:13,512
（托马斯上校、维克少校）

769
01:06:15,014 --> 01:06:16,390
中心 我是海斯
Control, this is Hayes.

770
01:06:16,557 --> 01:06:19,435
这里有托马斯上校和维克少校
I have a Colonel Tomas and a Major Vicek.

771
01:06:19,602 --> 01:06:20,936
底盘没问题
Undercarriage is clean.

772
01:06:22,229 --> 01:06:23,230
后面没问题
Back's clean.

773
01:06:24,640 --> 01:06:25,473
上校
Colonel.

774
01:06:25,640 --> 01:06:26,333
少校
Major.

775
01:06:26,457 --> 01:06:27,387
没问题了
All clear.

776
01:06:40,247 --> 01:06:42,375
你很清楚程序 上校
You know the drill, colonel.

777
01:06:43,542 --> 01:06:46,128
炮弹碎片 塞尔维亚的地雷
Shrapnel. A Serbian landmine.

778
01:06:46,295 --> 01:06:49,298
他们找的比医生还仔细
They've spent more time looking at it than the doctor did.

779
01:06:52,802 --> 01:06:54,929
请走过来
Step through, please, sir.

780
01:06:58,849 --> 01:07:00,017
转身
Turn around.

781
01:07:03,479 --> 01:07:05,106
谢谢
Thank you.

782
01:07:09,610 --> 01:07:12,363
走过来 伸手 耐心是关键
Step through. Arms out. Patience is key.

783
01:07:12,530 --> 01:07:15,616
我来这两年了 其他人待了更久
I've been coming here for two years, others have been here longer.

784
01:07:15,783 --> 01:07:18,119
- 其他人是谁？ - 我不知道
- What others? - I don't know.

785
01:07:18,285 --> 01:07:21,455
不过你是最行的 我是最差的
But you were the best of us and I was the least.

786
01:07:21,622 --> 01:07:25,084
这里一定还有其他人来完成大业
There must be others, here to finish what we begin.

787
01:07:25,251 --> 01:07:26,961
托马斯上校 很高兴再见到你
Colonel Tomas. Good to see you again.

788
01:07:27,120 --> 01:07:28,648
- 维克少校  - 幸会
- Major Vicek. - Pleasure.

789
01:07:28,711 --> 01:07:31,644
你们有两分钟检查北约的观点
You'll have minutes to preview NATO's point of view before the meeting.

790
01:07:32,925 --> 01:07:35,761
泰德 你的探员绍特
Now, Ted, your Russian CI agent, Salt.

791
01:07:36,284 --> 01:07:37,696
对于她 你有什么情报？
What can you tell us about her?

792
01:07:37,823 --> 01:07:39,594
我们认为她可能是苏联密探
We think she may be a Soviet plant,

793
01:07:40,300 --> 01:07:41,630
数年前被安插进来
inserted years ago

794
01:07:41,693 --> 01:07:45,140
为KGB的某个“毁灭日”做准备
in preparation for something the KGB called Day X.

795
01:07:45,332 --> 01:07:47,597
那一天 要开启大规模攻击
A day marking the start of a large strike

796
01:07:47,666 --> 01:07:49,480
对付美国及其盟友们
against the U.S. and her allies.

797
01:07:56,991 --> 01:07:59,243
这应该是总统了
This should be the president now.

798
01:08:02,163 --> 01:08:04,373
你有个艰巨的任务 契诃夫
You have a big job, Chenkov,

799
01:08:04,540 --> 01:08:05,833
不过你行的
but you can do it.

800
01:08:06,167 --> 01:08:08,335
你还没告诉我 你的任务是什么
You still haven't told me what your job is.

801
01:08:08,627 --> 01:08:10,379
家
Home.

802
01:08:10,671 --> 01:08:12,298
我要回家
I'm going home.

803
01:08:15,843 --> 01:08:18,137
- 趴下！找掩护！ - 保护总统！
- Down! Take cover! - Get the president!

804
01:08:18,763 --> 01:08:20,765
- 枪！他有枪！ - 退后！
- A gun! He's got a gun! - Get back!

805
01:08:22,099 --> 01:08:23,309
退后！
Get back!

806
01:08:36,781 --> 01:08:37,948
- 你没事吧？  - 没事
- Are you okay, sir? - Yes.

807
01:08:38,110 --> 01:08:38,932
该死
Goddamn it.

808
01:08:39,048 --> 01:08:40,610
依照程序 酋长前往地下碉堡
Geronimo is SOP, downward mobile.

809
01:08:46,373 --> 01:08:47,500
救命！这里！
Help, over here!

810
01:08:49,752 --> 01:08:52,046
快叫医护人员
Get a medic! Get a medic!

811
01:08:59,053 --> 01:09:01,180
我想我看到她了
I think I saw her.

812
01:09:01,597 --> 01:09:03,224
你看到谁？
You saw who?

813
01:09:05,059 --> 01:09:06,477
绍特
Salt.

814
01:09:07,603 --> 01:09:09,230
我想我在走廊上看到她了
I think I saw her in the corridor.

815
01:09:11,732 --> 01:09:13,275
另一位北约军官
The other NATO officer.

816
01:09:16,695 --> 01:09:17,905
她在这里
She's here.

817
01:09:19,406 --> 01:09:20,574
确认
Check.

818
01:09:20,741 --> 01:09:22,117
- 安全 - 走
- Clear. - Move.

819
01:09:22,827 --> 01:09:23,869
快！
Go!

820
01:09:24,036 --> 01:09:26,622
我们看见第二位攻击者 伊芙·绍特
We may have a visual on a second assailant. Evelyn Salt.

821
01:09:26,780 --> 01:09:28,480
伊芙·绍特在警戒区内
Repeat: Evelyn Salt on premises.

822
01:09:28,540 --> 01:09:29,950
一身北约军官打扮
May be dressed as a NATO officer.

823
01:09:30,910 --> 01:09:32,195
这不是演习
This is not a drill.

824
01:09:32,369 --> 01:09:34,420
白宫正遭受攻击
The White House is under attack.

825
01:09:34,588 --> 01:09:38,467
请前往最近出口 立刻依序离开
If you are near an exit, please proceed outside in an orderly manner.

826
01:09:38,634 --> 01:09:40,427
这不是演习
This is not a drill.

827
01:09:40,928 --> 01:09:43,264
我要确保这条走廊安全无虞
I need this hallway cleared to the left, now!

828
01:09:44,598 --> 01:09:47,560
中心 请求启动地下调堡
Command, this is Jenks. I need the PEOC bunker up and running.

829
01:09:47,726 --> 01:09:50,104
这若是俄罗斯政府授权的行动
If this was authorized by the Russian government,

830
01:09:50,271 --> 01:09:52,815
这就是战争行为 我们会复仇
it is an act of war, and we will respond.

831
01:09:54,108 --> 01:09:58,237
请前往最近出口 立刻依序离开
If you are near an exit, please proceed outside in an orderly manner.

832
01:09:58,404 --> 01:10:00,322
这不是演习
This is not a drill.

833
01:10:00,489 --> 01:10:02,157
- 安全！ - 走吧 长官
- Clear! - Let's go, sir.

834
01:10:04,869 --> 01:10:06,453
A小队 行动
Alpha team!

835
01:10:10,165 --> 01:10:11,792
快 快
Move, move.

836
01:10:12,459 --> 01:10:13,794
关上
Close it.

837
01:10:14,128 --> 01:10:15,462
关上
Close it.

838
01:10:23,095 --> 01:10:25,472
立刻依序离开
Please proceed outside in an orderly manner.

839
01:10:25,639 --> 01:10:27,725
这不是演习
This is not a drill.

840
01:10:58,797 --> 01:11:00,215
快 快
Go, go.

841
01:11:02,134 --> 01:11:04,678
酋长五秒内抵达惆堡门口
Geronimo approaching bunker door in five seconds.

842
01:11:09,433 --> 01:11:10,809
安全
Clear.

843
01:11:18,817 --> 01:11:20,069
她会跟来吗？
Any chance she could follow?

844
01:11:20,235 --> 01:11:22,321
门一关上 连我的人都进不来
My own men couldn't get through that door.

845
01:11:22,488 --> 01:11:25,157
是啊 可惜她不是你的人
Yeah, well, unfortunately, she isn't one of yours.

846
01:11:29,536 --> 01:11:30,537
好了 走
Okay, go.

847
01:11:32,206 --> 01:11:34,041
等门关好再走
Stay until it's shut and sealed.

848
01:11:37,962 --> 01:11:39,922
酋长安全
Geronimo secured.

849
01:12:08,367 --> 01:12:10,369
- 帮我接梅德福局长 － 是 长官
- Get me Director Medford. - Yes, sir.

850
01:12:11,203 --> 01:12:14,248
我想我们该严重考虑
Sir, I think we need to seriously consider the possibility

851
01:12:14,415 --> 01:12:17,292
今天 现在 就是毁灭日的开始
that today, right now, could be the start of Day X.

852
01:12:18,002 --> 01:12:20,504
总统先生 梅德福局长上线了
Mr. President, Director Medford is up.

853
01:12:21,755 --> 01:12:23,257
局长 情况如何？
Marion, what's the situation?

854
01:12:23,424 --> 01:12:26,427
资料应该正显示在您的屏幕上
It should be coming up on one of your screens.

855
01:12:26,969 --> 01:12:29,263
这里显示西伯利亚的移动飞弹
What you see there represents temperature drops

856
01:12:29,430 --> 01:12:31,598
温度下降
in mobile missile units in Siberia.

857
01:12:32,099 --> 01:12:35,602
这表示俄罗斯正在部署飞弹
It means the Russians are deploying their missiles to the field.

858
01:12:35,769 --> 01:12:39,356
地面人员己确认此事 总统先生
And that's been confirmed on the ground, Mr. President.

859
01:12:40,524 --> 01:12:44,028
我强烈建议提升战备到二级状态
Mr. President, I strongly recommend we go from DEFCON 4 to DEFCON 2.

860
01:12:44,194 --> 01:12:46,613
至少在前线是如此
At least at our forward bases.

861
01:12:48,282 --> 01:12:49,408
就这么办
Do it.

862
01:12:49,908 --> 01:12:51,952
由于俄罗斯已部署飞弹
And since the Russians have deployed,

863
01:12:52,745 --> 01:12:55,873
我们要考虑核武器攻击的可能
we need to look at our own nuclear attack options.

864
01:12:56,290 --> 01:12:59,126
不认真考虑 就无法遏阻他们
It's not on the table, it's not a deterrent.

865
01:13:00,794 --> 01:13:03,172
谢了 局长 我们会再联络你
Thanks, Marion. We'll come back to you.

866
01:13:23,442 --> 01:13:24,985
长官
Sir.

867
01:13:27,988 --> 01:13:31,116
外门卡住了 没有反应
The outer portal door is jammed. No response.

868
01:13:31,283 --> 01:13:34,036
大部分的监视器也失灵了
And we just lost the feed from most of our security cameras.

869
01:13:34,203 --> 01:13:36,830
我们看不见 不过没人能进来
We're blind down here and no one can enter this facility.

870
01:13:36,990 --> 01:13:38,422
指挥部 信号无法传输
Command, our eyes are down.

871
01:13:38,520 --> 01:13:41,539
地下调堡的安全外门也有故障
We have a PEOC outer security door malfunction.

872
01:13:41,585 --> 01:13:43,253
快点离开
Get out there now.

873
01:13:43,420 --> 01:13:45,297
封住这个房间
Seal this room.

874
01:13:47,382 --> 01:13:48,967
那条走廊 确认清楚
Down that corridor. Secure it.

875
01:14:34,054 --> 01:14:36,723
受害者被送往华盛顿医院
Victims are being taken to George Washington Hospital.

876
01:14:36,890 --> 01:14:40,936
据报白宫也有伤亡
Reports are coming in that there are casualties at the White House.

877
01:14:42,437 --> 01:14:44,189
我是霍华德·路易斯总统
This is President Howard Lewis.

878
01:14:44,350 --> 01:14:46,179
进行认证
Proceed with authentication.

879
01:14:46,314 --> 01:14:48,190
是 总统先生
Yes, Mr. President.

880
01:14:52,406 --> 01:14:54,324
准备开始认证
Ready to commence authentication.

881
01:14:54,491 --> 01:14:55,492
Z
Zulu.

882
01:14:55,650 --> 01:14:56,852
- T  - E
- Tango. - Echo.

883
01:14:56,993 --> 01:14:58,044
- S  - N
- Seven. - Niner.

884
01:14:58,187 --> 01:14:59,431
- J  - X
- Juliett. - X-ray.

885
01:14:59,525 --> 01:15:00,662
- S  - S
- Sierra. - Seven.

886
01:15:00,800 --> 01:15:01,812
- A  - M
- Alfa. - Mike.

887
01:15:01,988 --> 01:15:03,410
- C  - W
- Charlie. - Whiskey.

888
01:15:03,520 --> 01:15:04,580
- 五  - 六
- Five. - Six.

889
01:15:04,653 --> 01:15:05,357
T
Tango.

890
01:15:05,919 --> 01:15:07,880
认证密码确认
Authentication codes confirmed.

891
01:15:08,589 --> 01:15:10,424
一切交给你了 总统先生
It's all yours now, Mr. President.

892
01:15:11,049 --> 01:15:12,301
上帝与你同在
God be with you.

893
01:15:14,094 --> 01:15:17,139
攻击选项和目标由您控制
Attack options and targeting under your control, Mr. President.

894
01:15:17,306 --> 01:15:19,266
安德斯 纳布洛 你们在哪？
Anders and Nablo, what's your location?

895
01:15:20,392 --> 01:15:22,686
安德斯 纳布洛 你们在哪？
Anders and Nablo, what's your location?

896
01:15:24,396 --> 01:15:27,316
门外的监视器还能用吗？接上来
Is the camera outside this door working? Put it up.

897
01:15:27,482 --> 01:15:29,526
戴尔探员 报告情况
Officer Dryer, what's your status?

898
01:15:31,195 --> 01:15:32,279
戴尔探员 请说话
Officer Dryer, come in.

899
01:15:32,738 --> 01:15:35,240
联邦通讯委员会
Federal Communication Commission

900
01:15:35,407 --> 01:15:37,451
启动紧急警报系统
is activating the Emergency Alert System.

901
01:15:37,618 --> 01:15:39,203
那是什么？
Who the hell's that?

902
01:15:40,120 --> 01:15:42,915
是她 是伊芙·绍特
That's her. That's Evelyn Salt.

903
01:15:43,081 --> 01:15:44,791
她进来了 进入一级防卫
She's in. Go to DEFCON 1.

904
01:15:44,958 --> 01:15:46,460
把你的枪给我
Give me your side arm.

905
01:15:46,620 --> 01:15:47,517
不 长官
No, sir.

906
01:15:47,630 --> 01:15:50,130
总统身边只有特勤人员能持枪
Only Secret Service possess firearms in the president's vicinity.

907
01:15:50,297 --> 01:15:52,049
去它的规定 外面有敌人的间谍
Screw protocol. We got an enemy agent.

908
01:15:52,216 --> 01:15:54,176
规定就是规定
Protocol is protocol, sir.

909
01:15:54,509 --> 01:15:57,346
死人就是死人
And dead is dead.

910
01:15:58,096 --> 01:15:59,765
躲我后面！
Behind me!

911
01:16:01,141 --> 01:16:02,851
我是国家安全顾问
I'm the national security advisor.

912
01:16:03,310 --> 01:16:04,311
已经不是了
Not anymore.

913
01:16:12,277 --> 01:16:13,320
坐下
Sit down.

914
01:16:16,657 --> 01:16:17,699
你是谁？
Who are you?

915
01:16:18,242 --> 01:16:21,203
我的名字叫尼可莱塔寇夫斯基
My name, Mr. President, is Nikolai Tarkovsky.

916
01:16:22,454 --> 01:16:24,957
照我说的去做
And unless you do exactly as I say,

917
01:16:25,290 --> 01:16:27,668
否则我就是你最后看到的人
I will be the last person you will ever see.

918
01:16:33,674 --> 01:16:36,051
我们一起挑选攻击目标吧？
Shall we look at some selective attack options?

919
01:16:36,343 --> 01:16:37,678
你去死吧
Go to hell.

920
01:17:06,164 --> 01:17:09,418
攻击选项准备就绪
Selective attack options ready.

921
01:17:09,626 --> 01:17:11,044
泰德？
Ted?

922
01:17:11,211 --> 01:17:16,341
紧急行动讯息…
Emergency action message released by...

923
01:17:16,790 --> 01:17:19,953
恭喜 契诃夫同志 你成功了

924
01:17:20,345 --> 01:17:22,264
你怎么不告诉我？
Why didn't you tell me?

925
01:17:25,007 --> 01:17:27,043
我试过很多次 不过

926
01:17:27,801 --> 01:17:30,588
我的孤独是我唯一的朋友

927
01:17:30,772 --> 01:17:33,483
你没跟我们一起 我不会忘记你的
You weren't with us in Russia. I would have remembered you.

928
01:17:33,640 --> 01:17:35,596
我比你早一期

929
01:17:36,059 --> 01:17:38,050
奥洛夫摩下最闪亮的星星

930
01:17:38,520 --> 01:17:41,136
现在我很荣幸能发动攻击

931
01:17:41,523 --> 01:17:43,059
抱歉

932
01:17:43,785 --> 01:17:47,289
选择攻击目标
Selective attack targets acquired.

933
01:17:48,582 --> 01:17:50,083
德黑兰
Tehran.

934
01:17:50,417 --> 01:17:51,835
麦加
Mecca.

935
01:17:52,586 --> 01:17:55,630
麦加？德黑兰？
Mecca? Tehran?

936
01:17:55,788 --> 01:17:57,449
我们计划的第二步

937
01:17:57,623 --> 01:17:59,579
杀死九百万人

938
01:18:00,292 --> 01:18:01,748
激怒十亿穆斯林教徒

939
01:18:02,753 --> 01:18:04,744
美国会死的很难

940
01:18:04,931 --> 01:18:07,132
行动许可连结
Permissive action links initiated.

