01:19:27,050 --> 01:19:28,361
众人都认为已死的人
The man we thought was dead

962
01:19:28,420 --> 01:19:31,613
奇迹似地复活了
has made a resurrection that is miraculous.

963
01:19:31,748 --> 01:19:33,890
马特维耶夫总统还活着
President Matveyev is alive.

964
01:19:34,060 --> 01:19:35,420
前往俄罗斯现场
We're going to Russia.

965
