您所看到的是俄罗斯马特维耶夫总统
What you are seeing are live pictures of Russian president Matveyev

966
01:19:38,980 --> 01:19:41,379
正抵达莫斯科近郊机场
arriving at the airport outside of Moscow.

967
01:19:41,475 --> 01:19:43,131
这太惊人了
This is astonishing.

968
