据他的医生说
According to his doctors,

969
01:19:44,684 --> 01:19:46,240
马特维耶夫总统的乌龙死亡
President Matveyev's mistaken death

970
01:19:46,400 --> 01:19:49,026
归因于一种暂时性麻痹
is attributed to a temporary paralysis

971
01:19:49,142 --> 01:19:51,490
是由蜘蛛毒液萃取出的毒素引发的
from a toxin derived from spider venom.

972
01:19:51,705 --> 01:19:55,876
回顾一下，为了那些可能没有关注当天事件的人…
A recap for those who may not have been following the events of the day...

973
01:19:59,045 --> 01:20:01,131
至少我没弄错
At least I was right.

974
01:20:04,009 --> 01:20:07,512
我当时就觉得在北韩已经失去你了
I had a feeling we'd lost you back there in North Korea.

975
01:20:07,804 --> 01:20:11,558
我看得出麦克英勇的王子行动让你有多感动
I could see how moved you were by Mike's little white-knight routine.

976
01:20:11,725 --> 01:20:13,894
你应该要招募他
You were supposed to recruit him, Ev,

977
01:20:14,060 --> 01:20:15,687
不是爱上他
not fall in love with him.

978
01:20:16,897 --> 01:20:19,065
所以我叫奥洛夫去逮他
That's why I told Orlov to pick him up.

979
01:20:21,568 --> 01:20:23,778
对了 麦克好吗？
By the way, how is Mike?

980
01:20:25,739 --> 01:20:27,866
奥洛夫死了
Orlov is dead.

981
01:20:32,329 --> 01:20:34,581
那真是好消息
Well, that's good news.

982
01:20:34,873 --> 01:20:36,291
省了我的麻烦
Saved me the trouble.

983
01:20:38,000 --> 01:20:39,718
我得真的扭断他的手
I had to practically twist his arm

984
01:20:39,770 --> 01:20:41,925
才能逼他去中情局揭穿你的身份
to get him to blow your cover at the CIA.

985
01:20:44,210 --> 01:20:45,351
你明白
You see,

986
01:20:45,773 --> 01:20:47,710
他希望事情结束后 你能活命
he wanted you to come out of this thing alive.

987
01:20:51,056 --> 01:20:53,183
不过你需要有人垫背
But you needed somebody to take the blame.

988
01:20:54,392 --> 01:20:56,436
我是替死鬼
I'm the patsy.

989
01:20:59,773 --> 01:21:02,108
而我是英雄
And I'm the hero.

990
01:21:04,444 --> 01:21:06,780
恭喜了 伊芙
Congratulations, Ev.

991
01:21:08,448 --> 01:21:10,992
你即将红遍天下
You're about to become famous.

