义勇兵三型飞弹电力满载
Minuteman III ICBMs' batteries up to power.

997
01:23:08,902 --> 01:23:11,196
授权 99%
Authorization, 99 percent.

998
01:23:18,078 --> 01:23:19,371
快！
Go!

999
