请求许可发射
Permission to launch.

1003
01:23:55,448 --> 01:23:56,783
趴下 快！
Get down on the floor, now!

1004
01:23:57,575 --> 01:23:58,952
我叫你趴下！
I said now!

1005
01:24:03,957 --> 01:24:06,918
发射程序解除 系统恢复
Launch sequence aborted. Systems restored.

1006
01:24:07,085 --> 01:24:08,962
- 快 快 快！ - 把手举起来
- Move, move, move! - Show me your hands!

1007
01:24:09,129 --> 01:24:10,922
- 趴下！ - 你叫什么名字？
- Get down! - What is your name, sir?

1008
01:24:11,089 --> 01:24:14,426
我是中情局的温特 快救总统
I'm Theodore Winter, CIA. Help the president.

1009
01:24:15,927 --> 01:24:17,804
总统先生
Mr. President.

1010
01:24:19,264 --> 01:24:21,558
总统先生 你听得见吗？
Mr. President, can you hear me?

1011
01:24:23,351 --> 01:24:24,811
- 别动 - 急救小组马上到
- Hold still. - EMT's on the way.

1012
01:24:24,978 --> 01:24:27,105
- 送尸袋来  - 至少有七人死亡
- Make sure they got body bags. - At least seven.

1013
01:24:27,272 --> 01:24:28,815
她穿着防弹背心
She's wearing a vest.

1014
01:24:29,525 --> 01:24:31,980
五分钟后会议室见 我要清理一下
I'll meet you in five minutes. I wanna get cleaned up.

1015
01:24:32,152 --> 01:24:33,737
我要她单独关一间房
And I want her alone in a room.

1016
01:24:33,903 --> 01:24:36,364
我要她供出其他的俄国密探
If there are other KAs out there, I want her talking.

1017
01:24:36,570 --> 01:24:37,638
她不会说的
She won't talk.

1018
01:24:37,886 --> 01:24:40,160
她受过训练 无论如何都不会说
She's trained not to, no matter what we do to her.

1019
01:24:40,326 --> 01:24:42,620
我们要找这些人 就得自己找
If we're gonna find these people, we gotta do it.

1020
01:24:42,787 --> 01:24:44,998
有人已经动手 至少清了一部分
Somebody already did. At least some of them.

1021
01:24:45,165 --> 01:24:48,042
东河船上 12名死者 包括奥洛夫
Barge on the East River. Twelve dead, including Orlov.

1022
01:24:48,460 --> 01:24:49,878
是谁干的？
Who did that?

1023
01:24:52,005 --> 01:24:54,007
不知 鉴证小组正在调查
Don't know. Forensics are on it.

1024
01:25:01,473 --> 01:25:04,350
禁止进出，直到总统安全，退后
No one comes through until the president is secure. Step back.

1025
01:25:04,517 --> 01:25:06,770
- 我是西奥多·温特…  - 请退后，先生
- I'm Theodore Winter... - Step back, sir. Please.

1026
01:25:10,600 --> 01:25:11,823
先生 你受伤了
Well, sir, you're injured.

1027
01:25:11,914 --> 01:25:14,860
为何不坐下来？我们会照顾你
Why don't you have a seat? We'll take a look at you.

1028
01:25:15,528 --> 01:25:17,238
你还好吗？
Are you okay?

1029
01:25:18,072 --> 01:25:20,450
伤口很深
Pretty good gash there.

1030
01:25:20,617 --> 01:25:23,203
看来里面有玻璃
Looks like you got a piece of glass in there.

1031
01:25:44,891 --> 01:25:46,976
她又杀人了
She killed someone else.

1032
01:25:47,143 --> 01:25:49,687
是泰德温特 你最好快上来
It's Winter. It's Ted Winter, sir. You better get up here.

1033
01:25:59,030 --> 01:26:00,907
快看看他！
Check him. Check him!

1034
01:26:01,741 --> 01:26:02,742
检查生命迹象
Checking vitals.

1035
01:26:02,909 --> 01:26:05,745
我摸不到脉搏
I'm not getting a pulse. I'm not getting much.

1036
01:26:28,893 --> 01:26:30,562
坐下
Sit down.

1037
01:26:32,038 --> 01:26:34,714
飞行的15分钟内 她是你的
She's yours for 15 minutes during the flight.

1038
01:26:34,783 --> 01:26:36,940
- 把手给我  - 之后就是联邦调查局的
- Give me your hands. - Then she's the FBI's.

1039
01:27:24,157 --> 01:27:25,742
为什么要杀他？
Why'd you kill him?

1040
01:27:26,034 --> 01:27:27,493
因为一定要有人动手
Because somebody had to.

1041
01:27:41,007 --> 01:27:42,133
什么？
What?!

1042
01:27:53,144 --> 01:27:56,064
我猜你认为人人都表里如一
By this, I take it you think everybody is who they say they are.

1043
01:27:57,315 --> 01:27:59,859
你在奥洛夫投诚时就觉得有问题
You knew something was wrong the moment Orlov walked in.

1044
01:28:00,026 --> 01:28:01,486
我也是
So did I.

1045
01:28:01,653 --> 01:28:03,947
我们只是不知道是什么
We just didn't know what it was.

1046
01:28:04,626 --> 01:28:05,528
温特知道
Winter did.

1047
01:28:06,002 --> 01:28:06,982
温特？
Winter?

1048
01:28:09,243 --> 01:28:12,455
你要我相信是温特要发射飞弹？
You expect me to believe that Winter was gonna launch the missiles

1049
01:28:12,622 --> 01:28:14,540
而你拯救了全世界？
and you saved the world?

1050
01:28:16,167 --> 01:28:18,836
我要你相信 对
I would like you to believe that, yeah.

1051
01:28:20,672 --> 01:28:22,215
这是很大的指控
That's a big accusation.

1052
01:28:23,383 --> 01:28:24,717
反正
Well,

1053
01:28:25,802 --> 01:28:28,596
他死了 死无对证
he's dead now so he can't defend himself.

1054
01:28:28,805 --> 01:28:32,058
我想你必须自己决定
I guess you'll just have to decide for yourself.

1055
01:28:39,232 --> 01:28:41,192
有多少像你一样的人？
How many more like you are there?

1056
01:28:41,734 --> 01:28:43,444
像我？
Like me?

1057
01:28:44,529 --> 01:28:46,280
没有
None.

1058
01:28:46,906 --> 01:28:48,366
像他的？
Like him?

1059
01:28:48,533 --> 01:28:50,910
多到你我都无法对付
More than you or I can handle alone.

1060
01:28:53,570 --> 01:28:54,874
你真以为
You really think...

1061
01:28:55,010 --> 01:28:58,742
训练精良的苏联密探杀不了这位俄罗斯总统吗？
a trained Soviet agent couldn't kill the Russian president 

1062
01:28:58,835 --> 01:29:01,040
在近距离如果她想的话
 at point-blank range if she wanted to?

1063
01:29:05,174 --> 01:29:07,427
或是无法杀你
Or you, for that matter.

1064
01:29:08,136 --> 01:29:10,430
葬礼那天我可以杀你却没动手
I could've killed you at the funeral and I didn't.

1065
01:29:10,930 --> 01:29:13,474
你投降是因为我让你别无选择
You surrendered to me because I gave you no choice.

1066
01:29:13,641 --> 01:29:15,560
你很清楚
You know better.

1067
01:29:16,561 --> 01:29:18,813
我有选择
I had a choice.

1068
01:29:19,439 --> 01:29:20,606
你很清楚
You know better.

1069
01:29:27,388 --> 01:29:32,601
（奥洛夫死亡现场发现绍特指纹）

1070
01:29:40,793 --> 01:29:43,087
要是我相信你
If I did believe you,

1071
01:29:43,254 --> 01:29:47,050
我不是说我信你 只是就算我信
and I'm not saying for a second that I do, but if I did,

1072
01:29:48,968 --> 01:29:50,678
别人也不会信
nobody else would.

1073
01:29:52,305 --> 01:29:55,516
也许你可以换个角度想
Well, maybe you can think of a way around that.

1074
01:30:06,819 --> 01:30:09,405
他们夺走了我的一切
They took everything from me.

1075
01:30:11,157 --> 01:30:12,950
我要宰了他们
I'll kill them.

1076
01:30:27,006 --> 01:30:29,342
预计到达时间为四分钟
ETA, four minutes.

1077
01:30:36,390 --> 01:30:37,475
瞎扯！
Bullshit!

1078
01:30:49,904 --> 01:30:53,199
我们正飞往波托马克河西南方
We are approaching the Potomac, heading due south and west.

1079
01:30:58,871 --> 01:31:00,540
宰了他们！
Go get them.

1080
01:31:20,893 --> 01:31:22,019
绍特！
Salt!

1081
01:31:30,695 --> 01:31:34,157
绕回去！绕回去！
Circle back! Circle back!

1082
